name: Twins
rule_text: The word must contain at least one repeated letter (the same letter appears twice or more).

name: Bookworms
rule_text: The word must have exactly 5 letters.

name: Night Owls
description: For those who thrive in darkness.
rule_text: The word must contain the letter 'O'.

name: The Mirror
description: What you see is what you get — reversed.
rule_text: The word must be a palindrome (reads the same forwards and backwards).

name: Vowel Kingdom
description: A royal gathering of open sounds.
rule_text: The word must start with a vowel (A, E, I, O, U).

name: The Silents
rule_text: The word must contain a silent letter (e.g., 'k' in knife, 'b' in lamb).

name: Compound Crew
description: Two become one at this gathering.
rule_text: The word must be a compound word (two smaller words combined).

name: The Alphabet
description: Order is everything at this soirée.
rule_text: The letters in the word must be in alphabetical order.

name: Rhyme Time
rule_text: The word must rhyme with the previously accepted word. The first word can be anything.

name: The Zoo
rule_text: The word must contain the name of an animal within it (e.g., 'cat' in 'category').

name: Double Agents
rule_text: The word must contain at least one double consonant (e.g., 'ff', 'ss', 'tt', 'll').

name: The Evens
rule_text: The word must have an even number of letters.
